	   <tr><td colspan=2>&nbsp;&nbsp;The Crystalline Silk Threads (Are NO DROP)out of Velks lab they look like Pearl Necklaces, best is to carry a large Sewing kit &amp; just Combine every 5 you get into 1 Crystalline Fiber (NO DROP &amp; triv 51), then banking them till you get bile that way you only need 15 Crystalline Fibers insted of 75 Silk threads.  <br>  I have Killed 3 days gotten ONE Glowing Bile in GD (NO DROP &amp; Looks like a Foraged Rabbit) and promtly Combined it with 3 Fibers to get a Glowing Silk Piece.   One down 4 to go  :( <br><br>&nbsp;<br>Pearlay Griffinrider<br>Woodelf Ranger on ECI</td></tr>
